```markdown
# Remember-Me-AI

Purpose-driven, soulful AI chat as a PWA, with Web Push notifications for humanity!

## How to run

### Backend
1. `cd backend`
2. `npm install`
3. Set your VAPID PUBLIC/PRIVATE keys in `server.js`
4. `node server.js`

### Frontend
1. `cd frontend`
2. `npm install`
3. `npm run build`
4. Serve frontend (e.g. `npx serve -s build` or use Netlify/Vercel)

## Features
- Installable PWA
- Web Push notifications with VAPID keys
- Soulful chat and real-time guidance
```

